marginal (<span class='cmr-12'>5 </span><span class='cmmi-12'>&lt; </span>ratio <span class='cmmi-12'>&lt; </span><span class='cmr-12'>10</span>); rose = punctuated (ratio <span class='cmmi-12'>&gt; </span><span class='cmr-12'>10</span>); grey = frozen (zero transitions in
all replicates). Blue circles with line: lower phase boundary <span class='cmmi-12'>β</span><sub>low</sub><sup><span class='cmsy-8'>∗</span></sup> (highest <span class='cmmi-12'>β </span>with non-frozen
